      • run

        public MMDecomposition run​(boolean addTransporterSubsystem)
        The overall method that creates a decomposition.

        Within this method, cloning and specific decomposition are performed, and, if appropriate, the transporter and default subsystems are computed and added.

        Parameters:
        addTransporterSubsystem - whether to add the transporter subsystem
        Returns:
        an MMDecomposition object representing the constructed decomposition
